OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,FThe Scottish Parliament is set to vote
OL,7,Fon whether to legalise assisted dying
OL,8,Fin Scotland.
OL,10,FMSP's will vote on Liam McArthur's
OL,11,FAssisted Dying for Terminally Ill
OL,12,FAdults (Scotland) Bill.
OL,14,FA close result is expected with all
OL,15,FMSPs being given a free vote, rather
OL,16,Fthan having to vote along party lines.
OL,18,FThe vote is expected to take place at
OL,19,Faround 10pm on Tuesday night.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
