CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773940276
OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the vote, Mr
OL,7,FMcArthur said: "I just hope my MSP
OL,8,Fcolleagues grasp this opportunity to
OL,9,Faddress a failing in the current law `
OL,10,Fthe ban on assisted dying, which is
OL,11,Fleaving a small but not insignificant
OL,12,Fnumber of dying Scots and their
OL,13,Ffamilies horrendous decisions."
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrat MSP added that
OL,16,Fthe Bill would be the "most heavily
OL,17,Fsafeguarded assisted dying law
OL,18,Fanywhere in the world."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
