PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773940276
OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,FThe First Minister, the Scottish
OL,7,FConservative leader Russell Findlay
OL,8,Fand the Labour leader Anas Sarwar have
OL,9,Fall said they will vote against the
OL,10,FBill.
OL,12,FDeputy First Minister Kate Forbes will
OL,13,Falso vote against the legislation.
OL,15,FShe said: "I will vote against
OL,16,FAssisted Dying because the Bill is now
OL,17,Friskier and less safe after MSPs
OL,18,Frejected critical safeguards and
OL,19,Foutsourced essential protections for
OL,20,Fdoctors to the UK Government."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
