PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773940276
OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,FITV Border has been hearing from both
OL,7,Fsides of the argument.
OL,9,F"It's not our place to play God."
OL,11,FPastor Mark Smith opposes the
OL,12,Flegislation.
OL,14,FHe said: "Christians realise that the
OL,15,Fsanctity of life is really important.
OL,16,FWe are created in the image of god
OL,17,Ftherefore life is really significant
OL,18,Fand that it's not our place to play
OL,19,Fgod.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773940276
OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,F"I don't think it will alleviate
OL,7,Fsuffering, I think it will actually
OL,8,Fincrease suffering. For people like
OL,9,Fme, in a position of caring, it will
OL,10,Fcreate more obstacles to care and it
OL,11,Fwill create more obstacles to bringing
OL,12,Fhope into peoples' lives, it's a kind
OL,13,Fof cop out."
OL,15,F"He wanted to go still the person he
OL,16,Fwas"
OL,18,FFor Jemma Lothian, seeing her dad die
OL,19,Fof stage 4 cancer has shaped her
OL,20,Fopinion on assisted dying.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
