OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773940276
OL,3,CScottish Parliament to vote on
OL,4,Cassisted dying legislation
OL,6,FShe said: "He wanted to go still the
OL,7,Fperson he was rather than decline and
OL,8,Fend up a shadow of a man full of
OL,9,Fcancer and everybody remembering him
OL,10,Flike that.
OL,12,F"He was very vocal about being for
OL,13,Fassisted dying. You should be able to
OL,14,Ftake control of your own fate.
OL,16,F"You don't want someone to lose all
OL,17,Ftheir dignity and have to suffer. It
OL,18,Fshould be an option."
